#, fuzzy
msgid "https://chatbudgie.superbudgie.com"
msgstr "https://chat.superbudgie.com"

#: class-chatbudgie.php:504
msgid ""
"Action Scheduler is unavailable. Please make sure no other plugin is loading "
"an incompatible copy."
msgstr ""
"Action Scheduler no está disponible. Asegúrate de que ningún otro plugin "
"esté cargando una copia incompatible."

#: class-chatbudgie.php:1441
msgid ""
"Hi, I'm ChatBudgie, assistant of the website. To use the chat feature, "
"please go to the plugin settings page to connect your ChatBudgie account."
msgstr ""
"Hola, soy ChatBudgie, el asistente del sitio web. Para usar el chat, ve a la "
"página de ajustes del plugin y conecta tu cuenta de ChatBudgie."

#: class-chatbudgie.php:1445
msgid "Hi, I'm ChatBudgie, assistant of the website. How can I help you today?"
